            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Aponia <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> Montana nomine Caesi Montani fili sui ex ar<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>enti</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/>libris C testamento suo poni iussit <expan><abbr>her</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> XX non <expan><abbr>ded</abbr><ex>uxerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der Oberseite 2 Dübellöcher zur Befestigung der Statue. (B): Chic García, AE 1988: C(ai); a[rg(enti)]; AE 1988: Z. 2: h(eredes).</p>
